{"tid":789201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"文字何價？10 元請槍代做暑期作業","createTime":"2018-08-22T05:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T09:15:26.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f422194ca3cbdc9be5a7fe434fa8d4d3a2306593","tid":789201,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"暑假已過了大半，未做暑期作業點算好？《晴報》發現網上不少「槍手」明目張膽招生意，部分更鬥賤價搶客，收費低見10元。<br />\n<br />\n有教師指學校多數只檢查作業是否完成，學生或會走灰色地帶。大律師指，聘請或當「槍手」做作業，已犯串謀詐騙罪。<br />\n<br />\n在Instagram常有「代做暑期作業」帖文，「槍手」更以「想快樂過暑假就是這麼容易」等宣傳吸客，如讀書報告按字收費，「$20/100字、$40/300字」。有「槍手」自稱由大學生團隊組成，亦有中五生加入戰團搵快錢。<br />\n<br />\n記者扮學生聯絡姓蘇女「槍手」，要求代做文憑試中文閱讀理解模擬試卷，她開價17元，自稱是Band 1學校中五生，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/665000/666226/sksinn20150805106_20150814_L_opt_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F665000%2F666226%2Fsksinn20150805106_20150814_L_opt_1024.jpg&h=b9f7896e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女「槍手」（右）交收作業，並收取酬勞，她手上挽着兩三袋代做的功課準備趕往交收。(相片來源：晴報)"},{"pid":"b79b81ea988d375153ab143ab0064ff2f9ba02f1","tid":789201,"uid":59192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:32:50.000Z","msg":"中五生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72106f3e187d63d7e505cd71bfeebbd8c017f2f","tid":789201,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f092447f26d29477316b277268af425ae15b2484","tid":789201,"uid":90174,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"e+d 00後懶到抄都廢撚事"},{"pid":"d436c66fcc4550994b316e6407583203f65aa176","tid":789201,"uid":31323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:18:15.000Z","msg":"去書局買本新嘅咪有答案<br />\n搬字過紙抄過去洗幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56766116345